            <h2><span class="lektore">IELTS</span> Writing exam format</h2>
            <p>The Writing component of the Academic version includes two tasks, and it lasts for 60 minutes. Topics are of general interest to, and suitable for
            anyone entering undergraduate or postgraduate studies or seeking professional registration. The Writing component of the
            General Training version includes two tasks which are based on topics of general interest, and it also lasts for 60 minutes.
            </p>
