    <section id="third" class="container-fluid">
        <h2>What are the <span class="ielts">tasks</span>?</h2>
        <div id="cards">
            <div class="cards">
                <span class="fa-stack fa-3x">
                    <i class="fa fa-circle-o fa-stack-2x"></i>
                    <strong class="fa-stack-1x">1</strong>
                </span>
                <div>
                    <h5>Academic task 1</h5>
                    <p>Candidates will be presented with a graph (e.g. bar graph, or a line graph), table, chart, or diagram and are asked to describe, summarize or explain the
                    information in their own words.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="cards">
                <span class="fa-stack fa-3x">
                    <i class="fa fa-circle-o fa-stack-2x"></i>
                    <strong class="fa-stack-1x">2</strong>
                </span>
                <div>
                    <h5>Academic task 2 </h5>
                    <p>Candidates will be asked to write an essay in response to a point of view, argument or problem, or on the merits and demerits of a subject. 
                        This essay must be written in a formal style.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="cards">
                <span class="fa-stack fa-3x">
                    <i class="fa fa-circle-o fa-stack-2x"></i>
                    <strong class="fa-stack-1x">1</strong>
                </span>
                <div>
                    <h5>General task 1</h5>
                    <p>Candidates will be presented with a situation and asked to write a letter requesting information or explaining the
                    situation. The letter may be personal, semi-formal or formal in style.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="cards">
                <span class="fa-stack fa-3x">
                    <i class="fa fa-circle-o fa-stack-2x"></i>
                    <strong class="fa-stack-1x">2</strong>
                </span>
                <div>
                    <h5>General task 2</h5>
                    <p>Candidates will be asked to write an essay in response to a point of view, argument or problem. The essay can be
                    slightly more personal in style than the Academic Writing Task 2 essay.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
